machine_start_gcode:
G28
SET_GCODE_OFFSET Z=-0.15 MOVE=1
LOAD_GCODE_OFFSET
;CLEAN_NOZZLE COOLDOWN=0
SET_GCODE_VARIABLE MACRO=_CLIENT_VARIABLE VARIABLE=custom_park_y VALUE=232
_GOTO_TRASH
;M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
;M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer]
BED_TEMP=[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
SET_GCODE_VARIABLE MACRO=_KAMP_Settings VARIABLE=purge_height VALUE={first_layer_height}
SET_GCODE_VARIABLE MACRO=_KAMP_Settings VARIABLE=purge_amount VALUE=20

START_PRINT EXTRUDER_TEMP=[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer]
LOAD_CELL_TARE
PLAY_MIDI FILE=Beverey_Hills_Cop.mid
SET_GCODE_OFFSET z=-0.15
LOAD_GCODE_OFFSET
SET_PRINT_STATS_INFO TOTAL_LAYER=[total_layer_count]

;CLEAR_NOZZLE EXTRUDER_TEMP=140 BED_TEMP=60
